  "subject": "Data pre-load to on cps-xnf-proxy start-up using liquibase",
  "commit_message": "Data pre-load to on cps-xnf-proxy start-up using liquibase\n\n1. Common change-log master used only to specify the different change sets.\n2. Specific change set created for each cps component like dataspace, schema-set, anchor and dataNode\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-173\nSigned-off-by: puthuparambil.aditya <aditya.puthuparambil@bell.ca>\nChange-Id: I9545f9ed8d9c4345dffa262017ee37f3a5d043db\n",
